N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 130.2 - Filing procedure

State Regulations
A copy of each local law to be filed with the department
shall be mailed or delivered to the department at its Albany office or
submitted to the department through an electronic filing system maintained and
authorized by the department. Notes
